org.symphonyoss.client.model

Class Chat

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.symphonyoss.client.model.Chat

  • public class Chat
extends java.lang.Object
    Chat is a core model that defines an active conversation between users. It includes the ability to register ChatListener callbacks, which are monitored by the ChatService. Once defined, make sure to add the chat model to the ChatService in order to receive events when a listeners are defined.
